### Playbook F: yfinance Price Outcome Data

```
Gate 1 — PROBE:
  URL: Via Python yfinance library
  Format: pandas DataFrame
  Auth: None
  Rate limits: Unofficial — can get throttled at ~2000 req/hr
  Size: ~50KB per ticker per year (1d bars)
  ⚠️ yfinance is NOT an official API — data could disappear

