  Flag: any days with volume = 0 (holidays misidentified?)

Gate 4 — STORE:
  data/external/yfinance/raw/  (NOT stored — re-fetchable)
  data/external/yfinance/clean/price_history.parquet
  data/external/yfinance/db/prices.db → table: daily_ohlcv

Gate 5 — VERIFY:
  Compare yfinance SPY close vs CBOE settlement for same dates
  Should match within ±$0.02 (rounding)
  Also compare vs our historical_cache/ CSVs where overlap exists
```

